ransition-transform duration-500 group-hover:scale-105\" data-alt=\"A modern canvas tote bag in off-white with delicate tan leather handles, casually draped over a minimal wooden stool in a sunlit room. Soft, warm morning light, light-mode aesthetic. Calm, relaxed, premium everyday carry style.\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCW2YFJdchUUGmj8P_kVxDYN6BbrKu6ZiBFFdACoHDVwpTAcVk74VeZtnNgdjRctnFLUwxVnn9gIPAM1GJITkfY-qrh4duxS921o4hEGwmkoZ2semOkHSoc-MsV_T22DXeo3T6CMi-uygPuYxh449LcSByzekdQd-yuUmiYQCnKzBPczB7cXv9Z3i6k4FCRx5UqCsxvs33SGPud2r93pNK2vP3gMN78qgnSKPbet4DcXTyiwSVUQH1eSA\">\n</div>\n<div>\n<h4 class=\"font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-background font-medium line-clamp-1\">Tote Bag Canvas</h4>\n<p class=\"font-body-sm text-body-sm text-text-muted mb-xs\">Algodón orgánico</p>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mt-sm\">\n<span class=\"font-headline-sm text-headline-sm text-primary\">$28.00</span>\n<button class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-surface-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-surface-variant hover:bg-primary hover:text-on-primary transition-colors\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\" data-icon=\"add\">add</span>\n</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</main>\n<!-- Footer -->\n<footer class=\"bg-surface-container dark:bg-bg-voice w-full py-xl px-base flex flex-col items-center gap-md border-t border-outline-variant/20 dark:border-border-muted mt-auto\">\n<span class=\"font-display-lg text-display-lg text-primary\">Aura</span>\n<div class=\"flex gap-lg\">\n<a class=\"font-util-mono-sm text-util-mono-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-text-muted hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-secondary-fixed transition-colors\" href=\"#\">Privacidad</a>\n<a class=\"font-util-mono-sm text-util-mono-sm text-on-surface-variant dark:text-text-muted hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-secondary-fixed transition-colors\" href=\"#\">Términos</a>\n<a class=\"font-util-mono-sm text-util-mono-sm te